{"tid":1600703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暴徒太子站建「靈堂」， 累街坊發噩夢","createTime":"2019-09-28T17:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:03:06.000Z","uid":226548,"like":45,"dislike":493,"uniUserReply":139,"replies":[{"pid":"811aba651fe75bcc958bb7c531086b1fc32f3652","tid":1600703,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/U655P22T1D786731F1DT20190928170206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F0928%2FU655P22T1D786731F1DT20190928170206.jpg&h=8c0b8b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間：2019年09月28日 <br />\n<br />\n  縱暴派的政治文宣、海內外黃媒&ldquo;洗腦&rdquo;式的假新聞，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>炮制&ldquo;8.31太子站死人&rdquo;，流言蜚語蠱惑人心。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n  有人信以為真，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仿如邪教&ldquo;信徒&rdquo;日日到太子站獻花悼念，造謠者設靈堂、搞獻花、晚晚燒衣</span></strong>，哭啼連連，不少陌生人到此跪拜，居民為保人身安全，繞路避走所謂的&ldquo;太子站靈堂&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>  &ldquo;阻住條路又跪又拜&rdquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> &ldquo;屋企旁邊無端有&lsquo;白事設靈&rsquo;，好唔吉利！&rdquo;60歲的劉太</span></strong>住在鄰近太子港鐵站已30多年，她慨嘆這裏原本是熱鬧、和諧共處的老社區，街坊街裏打招呼問好，但自從有人造謠&ldquo;太子站打死人&rdquo;，和諧社區都不復存在。<br />\n<br />\n  一個月來港鐵太子站B1出口被迫封閉，已對居民出入太子站極為不便，加上&ldquo;信徒&rdquo;將出口布置成&ldquo;仇警靈堂&rdquo;，擺花圈，設碑誌，無論日與夜，都有幾十人群聚摺衣紙、燒冥鏹，加上大批陌生人川流不息走來獻花拜祭，又上香又點蠟燭，街坊坦言怕怕。"},{"pid":"df6d3dfd175c683c2436c11b52cf3b4e597cf584","tid":1600703,"uid":226548,"like":7,"dislike":177,"score":-170,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:05:19.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;睇上去唔系一般市民，著曬黑衫，我見到佢的都會行快兩步！&rdquo;街坊劉太說，晚上更有不少外籍人士聚集，&ldquo;氣氛好詭異&rdquo;，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>這班來&ldquo;拜祭&rdquo;的黑衫人鬼話連篇，在大街大巷慘叫、哭泣，令社區陷入不安</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n  劉太說，&ldquo;靈堂&rdquo;位處彌敦道與太子道西的交界，是非常繁忙的路口，&ldquo;日日大批人聚集阻住條路，他們又跪又拜，放工時間人多到要見縫穿針，有時無辦法亦會路過。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  暴亂三個月至今未平息，社區氣氛極不和諧，&ldquo;去餐廳吃飯都會有口角月以來連續多晚被暴徒包圍，投擲汽油彈、堵路及縱火。劉太好幾晚失眠，就算睡著也會被吵醒。"},{"pid":"426151942c36aa55cfcd30d6c1fa4e78a85726eb","tid":1600703,"uid":148253,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"篇文邊到出，有冇link??"},{"pid":"5897d9422ee98b25c366b9af4456f1f6d1922eb7","tid":1600703,"uid":269515,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bveD3wH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbveD3wH.png&h=649f6b11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14c99484ca1f32fbd2fa43b9ca559b7168a4dc22","tid":1600703,"uid":226548,"like":3,"dislike":107,"score":-104,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:06:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>打亂作息 憂有意外</strong><br />\n<br />\n  <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">68歲的退休人士Sandy</span></strong>，住旺角警署對角，她說未見過太子這麼恐怖。她憶述8月31日晚從銅鑼灣回家，港鐵不停太子站，&ldquo;有錢都無車返，只好搭到南昌站落，從大角咀步行回家，我未試過唔識路返，好彩有同路人帶路&rdquo;，當晚行了約一小時，行到太子附近，見到很多暴徒被警察追捕，&ldquo;成群人衝過來，我好驚，只好走入人多地方暫避。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Sandy慨嘆暴亂已打亂生活作息，擔心回家途中或有意外</span></strong>，見到新聞報道有人包圍旺角警署，&ldquo;飯都唔食立即回家，取消老友記聚餐&rdquo;。Sandy說，&ldquo;我們都是尋常百姓，只想好好生活。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【編輯：刘凯程】"},{"pid":"102e59ce8c4187dfc489921ffe6a132aa7e7ee44","tid":1600703,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":33,"score":-32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/786731.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F0928%2F786731.shtml&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8rwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=40316c98\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/786731.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"646c4c5222f1acc8ccb86fe80230b30c41e068f6","tid":1600703,"uid":319806,"like":249,"dislike":1,"score":248,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"住殯儀館附近都未出聲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88ad5c67198e072615cbb3ed1b54240ba397d59","tid":1600703,"uid":90601,"like":179,"dislike":1,"score":178,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"黑警又TG又開槍又屌市民你唔驚 你驚燒衣?"},{"pid":"83f9020990e2bd00fe9f5260f20cdc1259b33d6a","tid":1600703,"uid":45910,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"102e59ce8c4187dfc489921ffe6a132aa7e7ee44","tid":1600703,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":33,"score":-32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/786731.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F0928%2F786731.shtml&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8rwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=40316c98\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/786731.shtml</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"太公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747d7bfcf7c6caa27bc2adb02f34b55ace2630a0","tid":1600703,"uid":148253,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"102e59ce8c4187dfc489921ffe6a132aa7e7ee44","tid":1600703,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":33,"score":-32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/786731.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F0928%2F786731.shtml&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8rwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=40316c98\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/786731.shtml</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:09:10.000Z","msg":"大公報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔止義士呀，周圍既朋友仔都會搞埋佢地呀!!!"},{"pid":"940e2121bdbf6c266ac99151d997c12436e2484f","tid":1600703,"uid":38904,"like":131,"dislike":1,"score":130,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"住太子站靈堂街坊噩夢 - <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大公報</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好post唔post係都要post大公報<br />\n仆街死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0a0ef84d0ed013260f33428821e42f73d37069","tid":1600703,"uid":149435,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"要怪怪黑警"},{"pid":"2610e55167d070bf9800bf6c4b3f350b459a4256","tid":1600703,"uid":282280,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"我屋企後面係墳場都未撚出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正見證過死亡既人，<br />\n係唔會覺得呢d事有幾得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（至少我唔覺）</span>"},{"pid":"10a54b043b75a3b78e787ff983f4580571e7e107","tid":1600703,"uid":105340,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"問題唔係市民<br />\n係政府 黑狗 黨鐵 唔肯公開完整無修改的CCTV片段<br />\n我地只係作出最壞可能<br />\n太子站一定死左人<br />\n而且可能將屍體留係漆黑的路軌入面<br />\n而且用埋長沙灣 荔枝角等站運送屍體<br />\n消防一定知道內情 杵狀 法師都一定知內情<br />\n如果你地唔講真相<br />\n阿鼻地獄都等緊你地<br />\n關二哥 耶穌 聖母 真主 都幫唔到你地"},{"pid":"55b4c0b88c81a7b4bf5147d7a0db41fb747affb3","tid":1600703,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"見親都好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「光 復 香 港」  廢 除 《 聯 合 聲 明 》 第 三 次 公 投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600396</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c465ce31c631487d63a45c6e9f99712db4a8b236","tid":1600703,"uid":10788,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;睇上去唔系一般市民，著曬黑衫，我見到佢的都會行快兩步！&rdquo;街坊劉太說<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁佢係唔係講粗口會打冷震既人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"67704b8d6f50561aee43febabff956af76e59dd7","tid":1600703,"uid":146865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"426151942c36aa55cfcd30d6c1fa4e78a85726eb","tid":1600703,"uid":148253,"like":69,"dislike