yTime":"2019-09-28T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/786731.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F0928%2F786731.shtml&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8rwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=40316c98\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/786731.shtml</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T20:39:39.000Z","msg":"香港CNA ，屌！"},{"pid":"8206759dd61c160359708aef16889071c182635b","tid":1600703,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T20:43:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;睇上去唔系一般市民，著曬黑衫，我見到佢的都會行快兩步！&rdquo;街坊劉太說，晚上更有不少外籍人士聚集，&ldquo;氣氛好詭異&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n九成係搵大陸人編稿再轉繁體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8537cb6619b22feab6348638269b5a1745ecf36","tid":1600703,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T20:44:32.000Z","msg":"平生不做虧心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8569f02921c04e51b9370c4c9fc751173424f5","tid":1600703,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T20:48:17.000Z","msg":"好L好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a45568d1c759af88a0c9573fbc8a09b0b434e0","tid":1600703,"uid":25743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T20:53:59.000Z","msg":"發噩夢？<br />\n68歲無聽個呢句？<br />\n「人心不作虧心事，半夜敲門也不驚」<br />\n如果發噩夢，証明心中有鬼導致有「愧」<br />\n睇嚟呢位街坊做咗啲唔光彩嘅事驚有「烈士」尋仇喎？<br />\n唔通係831黑警家屬？參加過撐警大會？定係太子黨鐡員工呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你係真唔信有人死咗起太子站，咁根本唔需要驚，因為根本就唔存在嘛，等於話明天太子站烈士顯靈出現毀滅港共，你根本唔會驚，因為無可能發生嘛，太子站無死人呀嘛，無發生嘅話又何來噩夢？除非真係真事或見過件事嘅人啫<br />\n紅報嘅大公報唔FC就借呢街坊作文報道，咁証明我地估中咗，大公報要借題出文維穩發生咗嘅事，點解我咁肯定？就如我所講，如果你係報社，我同你講要登新聞話我噩夢因為太子站有靈堂啊，正常人係會叫你去睇醫生唔會真係報出嚟傻比人笑掛，如果咁我都話有噩夢，係見到太子站烈士英靈啦。<br />\n嗱！心果有噩夢嘅街坊唔想咁樣好簡單，一齊幫831找回真相就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b68695a0fd8413f10917e2f3d5760dd3f21980","tid":1600703,"uid":252862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T21:00:09.000Z","msg":"又唔撚見我地會驚?<br />\n身有屎咪驚囉仆街"},{"pid":"c557a8671f932c1e66a735295dbadcc0c9f06728","tid":1600703,"uid":259246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T21:01:53.000Z","msg":"藍絲logic:係你心靈過份脆弱"},{"pid":"1cf57ac44d6481af1d9ef7fa834c11b68e2adb77","tid":1600703,"uid":203797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T21:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8hFyJS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8hFyJS.jpg&h=175f901c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張真係萬用"},{"pid":"ec5e5d72a1fade49f144e8d5b3a50ba66ecd1c0e","tid":1600703,"uid":244230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T21:03:30.000Z","msg":"做咩事咁心虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好人好者驚乜啊"},{"pid":"dbbc45f2a846d49d0d6e8bba3e4e4bdae7ed4489","tid":1600703,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T21:12:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;睇上去唔系一般市民，著曬黑衫，我見到佢的都會行快兩步！&rdquo;</span><br />\n屌佢都識講靈堂 佢去喪禮著紅色旗袍既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bc14af05a0c5e92bfa2c7c7c91bbf8a11d9e08","tid":1600703,"uid":18791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2610e55167d070bf9800bf6c4b3f350b459a4256","tid":1600703,"uid":282280,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"我屋企後面係墳場都未撚出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正見證過死亡既人，<br />\n係唔會覺得呢d事有幾得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/