\n<br />\n<br />\n【編輯：刘凯程】"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T19:46:58.000Z","msg":"唔停太子 所以去南昌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信個班 要弱智到咩地步<br />\n不過真係好多人信哩d弱智文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:25:01.000Z","msg":"😂大陸仔撚識香港地圖咩 不過我都好好奇要行幾耐"},{"pid":"f4480a6eaba14125b82068012ae81df1a3605d85","tid":1600703,"uid":297613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c465ce31c631487d63a45c6e9f99712db4a8b236","tid":1600703,"uid":10788,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;睇上去唔系一般市民，著曬黑衫，我見到佢的都會行快兩步！&rdquo;街坊劉太說<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁佢係唔係講粗口會打冷震既人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"見到紋身既人會嚇到瀨尿"},{"pid":"2c9713dd1d2d58ad593712f2c3d2b2c4932a1a6b","tid":1600703,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:35:22.000Z","msg":"平生不作虧心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日行過完全唔覺得驚，大家都係手足"},{"pid":"5f9c0fe6b7f5aca14fc5bd1e671827d340a1a30a","tid":1600703,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"又話行得正企得正 做咩要驚"},{"pid":"cd3ff0f42ab6f38db13bdb7f9fc9d0ce582346f5","tid":1600703,"uid":224755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"石硤尾發生咩事，大家都要了解下"},{"pid":"90e7fb3c3da1aec6f82d5c70c53e9983d65b35a3","tid":1600703,"uid":2480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f9c0fe6b7f5aca14fc5bd1e671827d340a1a30a","tid":1600703,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"又話行得正企得正 做咩要驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"做左虧心事先會驚"},{"pid":"6f08fc8a0316f6420a9460f5e0c881fa01c52a3a","tid":1600703,"uid":204872,"like":0,"dislike