":{"pid":"5897d9422ee98b25c366b9af4456f1f6d1922eb7","tid":1600703,"uid":269515,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bveD3wH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbveD3wH.png&h=649f6b11&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"仲有電車岀軌<br />\n寫住太子"},{"pid":"c6c4a6a9e7e6004e9c2cee788d1ea70ddafddf2f","tid":1600703,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"811aba651fe75bcc958bb7c531086b1fc32f3652","tid":1600703,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0928/U655P22T1D786731F1DT20190928170206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F0928%2FU655P22T1D786731F1DT20190928170206.jpg&h=8c0b8b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間：2019年09月28日 <br />\n<br />\n  縱暴派的政治文宣、海內外黃媒&ldquo;洗腦&rdquo;式的假新聞，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>炮制&ldquo;8.31太子站死人&rdquo;，流言蜚語蠱惑人心。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n  有人信以為真，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仿如邪教&ldquo;信徒&rdquo;日日到太子站獻花悼念，造謠者設靈堂、搞獻花、晚晚燒衣</span></strong>，哭啼連連，不少陌生人到此跪拜，居民為保人身安全，繞路避走所謂的&ldquo;太子站靈堂&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>  &ldquo;阻住條路又跪又拜&rdquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> &ldquo;屋企旁邊無端有&lsquo;白事設靈&rsquo;，好唔吉利！&rdquo;60歲的劉太</span></strong>住在鄰近太子港鐵站已30多年，她慨嘆這裏原本是熱鬧、和諧共處的老社區，街坊街裏打招呼問好，但自從有人造謠&ldquo;太子站打死人&rdquo;，和諧社區都不復存在。<br />\n<br />\n  一個月來港鐵太子站B1出口被迫封閉，已對居民出入太子站極為不便，加上&ldquo;信徒&rdquo;將出口布置成&ldquo;仇警靈堂&rdquo;，擺花圈，設碑誌，無論日與夜，都有幾十人群聚摺衣紙、燒冥鏹，加上大批陌生人川流不息走來獻花拜祭，又上香又點蠟燭，街坊坦言怕怕。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:03:25.000Z","msg":"講咁多野<br />\n小心搞你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baad3a686182dd7c2a31b26f201388f81e05c990","tid":1600703,"uid":20979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"由細到大我都好怕黑，好驚鬼，但太子我一d都唔驚。<br />\n<br />\n因為我知佢地係手足，係最正義嘅鬼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}